{"tid":1191987,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"Mclaren F1超跑的靈魂繼承車","createTime":"2019-06-08T07:59:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T07:59:56.000Z","uid":236926,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"cfef3a9090850ba810230b5fc22673a260c722f5","tid":1191987,"uid":236926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T07:59:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/o3dJciP5yP8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fo3dJciP5yP8&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8%2FE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=946d3b2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/o3dJciP5yP8</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XPO5yiy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXPO5yiy.jpg&h=1a2f8acb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nGordon Murray成立的汽車公司Gordon Murray Automotive，宣布將推出F1後繼作品T.50<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SbASXLh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSbASXLh.jpg&h=bb8af890&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n採用中置後驅佈局，搭載由Cosworth研發的3.9公升V12自然吸氣引擎，最大馬力有650匹，峰值扭力有45.9kgm，最高轉速設定在12,100rpm，並配以<span style=\"color: red;\">Xtrac六速手波。</span><br />\n<br />\n車廂是F1式的中央駕駛座設計，後方可容納兩位乘客，同Mclaren自家的Speedtail一樣。<br />\n車重只有980kg，車長4,380mm，車闊1,850mm<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jTQr2en.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjTQr2en.jpg&h=7c6465bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pukIEuzgd3U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpukIEuzgd3U&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8%2FE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=bac4698c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pukIEuzgd3U</a><br />\nT.50與F1一樣將配主動式空氣動力學裝置，並在車尾位置設有如當年Braham BT64B F1賽車般的大風扇協助製造positive downforce<br />\n<br />\n當年的BT64B賽車只參與過1978年瑞士格蘭披治，並由Niki Lauda以34秒距離得冠軍，但隨後即因其它車隊投訴而退賽<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/acq8BvIhUTg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Facq8BvIhUTg&d=Bm7f%2FS52JQW29R4IancW8%2FE18wtZo%2FyF0aYgy6X%2FhPY%3D&h=d2916924\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/acq8BvIhUTg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">T.50預計2022年出，限量生產100部</span></span>"}]}